postTimeline.postDescription: a picture of this years mascot, lenny and the capsule that we sent to space with the balloon
This is us climbing up an aviation control tower at Wendover air base. Some of us were a little scared of the height.
After a lot of hard work and dedication it all came down to this. The launch, we were all a little nervous but excited nonetheless.
After a successful launch the team has a little dance to  celebrate, even though we couldn't recover it . Seems all that hard work payed off
